{"id":52682,"title":"A rare cause of ascites: myxoedema ascites.","abstract":"The case report describes an 88-year-old patient who presented with new-onset ascites. After excluding frequent causes of ascites, he was diagnosed with myxoedema ascites. Myxoedema ascites is rare. Analysis of ascitic fluid shows a high serum-ascites albumin gradient and a high protein level. Myxoedema ascites resolves completely after starting thyroid hormone replacement therapy.","date":"2014-03-03","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24579248","annotations":[{"name":"Hormone replacement therapy (menopause)","weight":0.906247,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hormone_replacement_therapy_(menopause)"},{"name":"Ascites","weight":0.906012,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ascites"},{"name":"Thyroid hormone","weight":0.852262,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thyroid_hormone"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Hormone","weight":0.787886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hormone"},{"name":"Thyroid","weight":0.773888,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thyroid"},{"name":"Protein","weight":0.729208,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protein"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.605498,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Hormone therapy","weight":0.513143,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hormone_therapy"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.250192,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Myxedema","weight":0.162801,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myxedema"},{"name":"Albumin","weight":0.102124,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Albumin"},{"name":"Fluid","weight":0.0152163,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fluid"}]}
